---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
---

<Layout
  title="Kubernetes Recipes Book Signing"
  description="Meet Luca Berton at KubeCon Europe 2026 for two Kubernetes Recipes book signing events in Amsterdam."
>
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-4 py-16 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">

    <!-- Hero -->
    <div class="text-center mb-16">
      <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-100 px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-amber-800 mb-6">📚 KubeCon Europe 2026</span>
      <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">Kubernetes Recipes<br/>Book Signing</h1>
      <p class="text-xl text-gray-600 max-w-2xl mx-auto">Meet the author, get your copy signed, and talk Kubernetes strategy during KubeCon week in Amsterdam.</p>
    </div>

    <!-- Events -->
    <div class="space-y-8 mb-16">

      <!-- Event 1: Signal Overflow -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border-2 border-amber-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-amber-50 to-white p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-amber-600 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-white">EVENT 1</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-purple-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-purple-800">🎤 Meetup</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-teal-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-teal-800">📡 Observability</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Signal Overflow: Observability in the Age of AI</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-amber-700 font-semibold mb-6">Monday, March 23, 2026</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">🕐</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Time</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">18:30 – 21:00</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">📍</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Location</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Booking.com HQ</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Oosterdokskade 163, Amsterdam</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-amber-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">🎙️</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Hosted by</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">SRE NL</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Site Reliability Engineering Netherlands</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">KubeCon special by SRE NL at Booking.com — talks on OpenTelemetry best practices for large systems and observability in the AI-native age, plus food, networking, and <strong>Kubernetes Recipes book signing</strong>.</p>

        <div class="bg-amber-100/50 rounded-xl p-4 mb-6">
          <p class="text-sm text-amber-800"><strong>⚠️ Important:</strong> Bring a valid ID for building access.</p>
        </div>

        <a href="https://luma.com/o93w1hxi" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-amber-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-amber-700 transition-colors shadow-md hover:shadow-lg">RSVP on Luma →</a>
      </div>

      <!-- Event 2: vCluster Booth -->
      <div class="rounded-3xl border-2 border-violet-200 bg-gradient-to-br from-violet-50 to-white p-8 shadow-lg">
        <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3 mb-4">
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-violet-600 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-bold text-white">EVENT 2</span>
          <span class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-violet-100 px-3 py-1 text-xs font-semibold text-violet-800">☸ KubeCon Expo</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Kubernetes Recipes Book Signing at vCluster Booth</h2>
        <p class="text-sm text-violet-700 font-semibold mb-6">Tuesday, March 24, 2026</p>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-violet-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">🕐</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Time</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">12:30 – 13:30</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">KubeCon Day 1 Lunch Break</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-violet-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">📍</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Location</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">Booth #521</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">KubeCon Expo Floor, RAI Amsterdam</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
            <div class="flex-shrink-0 w-10 h-10 rounded-lg bg-violet-100 flex items-center justify-center text-lg">🤝</div>
            <div>
              <div class="text-xs text-gray-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Hosted at</div>
              <div class="font-semibold text-gray-900">vCluster Booth</div>
              <div class="text-sm text-gray-600">Virtual Clusters for Kubernetes</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Stop by the vCluster booth during the lunch break to meet Luca Berton, get your copy of <strong>Kubernetes Recipes</strong> signed, and chat about Kubernetes, platform engineering, and cloud-native strategy. No registration needed — just show up!</p>

        <div class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-violet-100 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-violet-800">No RSVP needed — just come by Booth #521</div>
      </div>

    </div>

    <!-- About the Book -->
    <div class="rounded-3xl bg-gray-900 p-8 sm:p-12 text-white mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4">About Kubernetes Recipes</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-300 mb-6">A practical guide to solving real-world Kubernetes challenges. Structured around reusable recipes for deployment, scaling, security, observability, high availability, and hybrid environments. Whether you are a developer looking for deployment patterns or a CTO thinking about platform strategy, the book meets you where you are.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://kubernetes.recipes/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-white px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors">Learn More →</a>
        <a href="/blog/kubernetes-recipes-mindset-cto-platform-strategy/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-gray-700 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-gray-600 transition-colors">Read: The Recipe Mindset →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- About Luca -->
    <div class="rounded-3xl border border-gray-200 bg-white p-8 sm:p-12 mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-4">About the Author</h2>
      <p class="text-gray-700 mb-6">Luca Berton is an AI & Cloud Advisor, co-author of Kubernetes Recipes, and speaker at KubeCon Europe 2026. He helps organizations turn cloud-native complexity into practical platform decisions that create business value.</p>
      <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4">
        <a href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/lucaberton/" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-blue-600 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-blue-700 transition-colors">Connect on LinkedIn →</a>
        <a href="/services/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-gray-100 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-bold text-gray-900 hover:bg-gray-200 transition-colors">Consulting Services →</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- More KubeCon -->
    <div class="text-center">
      <p class="text-gray-600 mb-4">Explore all KubeCon Europe 2026 events</p>
      <a href="/blog/kubecon-europe-2026-side-events/" class="inline-flex items-center rounded-xl bg-gray-900 px-8 py-4 text-sm font-bold text-white hover:bg-gray-700 transition-colors shadow-md">View All Side Events →</a>
    </div>

  </main>
</Layout>
